Jaha tak Mai samjha hun , 
Yeh jo duriya dikhayi deti hai 
Sunayi jati hain in do mulko Kay biich , yeh galat hai , kyonki na Pakistan ki Janta or na hi India ki Janta hate karna pasand karti hai , yeh to yeh namuradd neta hai jo humko bhadkatey hain ik doosrey Kay khilaaf ! Mujko koi Bata do ,kya ham alag dikhtay hain ? Kya hum alag pehantey hain ? Kya hum alag khana khatey hain ? 
Nahi na , to phir yeh sab dooriyan kyon ? 
Mai bhi Lahore ghoomna chahta hoon , Mai bhi Karachi ki galiyon may biryani khana chahta hun  or mujhe PURA yakin hai ki Pakistan banda bhi Delhi ghoomna chahta hai wo bhi Chandni chowk ki galiyon may laziz khana khana chahta hai , wo bhi Agra Mai taaz ka Didaar karna chahta hai , phir yeh netao ki nafrat kyon ? 
Ukhaad Kay phenk do esay netao Ko aisey maulwiyo Ko aisey pujario Ko jo hamarey bich nafrat failatey hain ! 
Lot's of love from delhi(India) to each and everyone in Pakistan !
